"    * Employee Details\n"
"    * Employee Contracts\n"
"    * Passport based Contract\n"
"    * Allowances/Deductions\n"
"    * Allow to configure Basic/Gross/Net Salary\n"
"    * Employee Payslip\n"
"    * Integrated with Leaves Management\n"
